Title: Parmigiani Fleurier Pershing 005 Chronograph Watch PFC528-1010101-HA1442
Description: Watches Jewelry Accessories About us Policies Parmigiani Fleurier Pershing 005 Chronograph Watch PFC528-1010101-HA1442 (Click to Enlarge) Parmigiani Fleurier Pershing 005 Chronograph Watch PFC528-1010101-HA1442 Condition: Unworn Brand: Parmigiani Fleurier Series: Pershing Gents Retail Price: $48,000.00 Reference: PFC528-1010101-HA1442 Also Known As: PFC5281010101HA1442 Web ID: 157565 Stock Number: 2188861 Case Size: 42 mm Gender: Gents Movement: Automatic Caliber: PF334 Bezel: 18K Rose Gold Functions: Hours, Minutes, Small seconds, Chronograph, Date Strap: Alligator Clasp Type: Deployment Signatures: Parmigiani Fleurier Included Items: Manufacturer's Box and Papers Power Reserve: 50 Hours Materials: 18K Rose Gold Finishing: 18K Rose Gold Case Back: Solid Dial Color: Silver Bringing an irresistible touch of elegance and style into the sporty, robust Pershing collection, Parmigiani Fleurier presents this magnificent timepiece which boasts an alluring appearance to go with the well-known precision and functionality. Made of 18K rose gold and featuring closed case back engraved with Pershing boat motif, the 42mm case offers 100m water resistance. Featuring central chronograph ¼ seconds hand and 30-minute and 12-hour counters along with hours, minutes, small seconds and date indication, the Côtes de Genève silver-colored dial ensures great legibility owing to its delta-shaped hands with luminescent coating and rose gold-plated appliqués. Beneath lies the self-winding PF334 caliber comprised of 303 parts, featuring two barrels, 68 jewels, "Côtes de Genève" decoration and bevelled bridges and providing 50-hour power reserve while beating at 28,800 v.p.h. The watch is worn on black alligator leather Hermès strap with deployment clasp.
